title: LaManna Direct
description: A large grocery store located in a shopping complex at Essendon Fields Airport, easily accessible to residents in the Northern Suburbs. Carries a large range of vegan grocery brands such as Gardein, Tofutti, So Delicious ice creams, Bio cheese, Linda McCartney, Sanitarium, along with milk alternatives (including fresh almond milk). Also sells other vegan specialties, along with the usual grocery items such as nuts, vegetables, bread and more.
